OL,3,CStrictly judge Shirley Ballas taken to
OL,4,Chospital after falling on glass table
OL,6,FStrictly Come Dancing's Shirley Ballas
OL,7,Fwas taken to hospital after falling
OL,8,Fand hitting her head on a glass table.
OL,10,FThe 65-year-old head judge on the BBC
OL,11,Fdancing programme said she was taking
OL,12,Ftime to heal her neck and back
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident, but had not
OL,14,Finjured her skull.
OL,16,FIn a story post on Instagram, Ballas
OL,17,Fsaid: "Thank you to all who reached
OL,18,Fout to see how I'm doing.
