OL,6,F"Scary fall backwards hitting my head
OL,7,Fon the glass dressing table. Trip to
OL,8,Fhospital to get a brain scan.
OL,9,FFortunately for me no cracked skull.
OL,11,F"I'll rest a few days to heal my neck
OL,12,Fand back.
OL,14,F"Hugs (and) thank you to
OL,15,F@barbara mccoll (a fellow professional
OL,16,Fdancer) for getting my emergency
OL,17,Fappointment and to Sammy Stopford (her
OL,18,Fex-husband) for taking me, and sitting
OL,19,Fwith me all day. Gratitude, as the
OL,20,Fdoctor said I was very lucky."
