OL,6,FBallas is due to take part in the
OL,7,FStrictly Come Dancing live tour with
OL,8,Ffellow judges Anton Du Beke and Craig
OL,9,FRevel Horwood when it begins next
OL,10,Fweek, with 30 shows scheduled until
OL,11,FFebruary 15.
OL,13,FThe Wirral-born star joined Strictly
OL,14,Fin 2017, and made her debut as head
OL,15,Fjudge in September that year.
OL,17,FBallas has used her platform to
OL,18,Fadvocate for male suicide awareness
OL,19,Fand men's mental health, after her
OL,20,Fbrother took his own life in 2003.
