OL,6,FShe is an ambassador for charities
OL,7,FCampaign Against Living Miserably and
OL,8,FSuicide&Co.
OL,10,FIn August last year, Ballas said she
OL,11,Fwill "never feel completely safe
OL,12,Fagain" after being targeted by a
OL,13,Fstalker who accused her of killing a
OL,14,Fmember of her family in an interview
OL,15,Fwith the Sunday Mirror.
